logs: create table logs (id serial not null constraint logs_pk primary key, data varchar(500) not null);
sellers: create table sellers (id serial not null constraint sellers_pk primary key, name varchar(200) not null, phone varchar(11) not null, email varchar(200) not null);
marketplaces: create table marketplaces (id serial not null constraint marketplaces_pk primary key, name varchar(200) not null, description varchar(600));
products: create table products (id serial not null constraint products_pk primary key, name varchar(200) not null, description varchar(500), price money not null);
categories: create table categories (id serial not null, name varchar(200) not null, description varchar(400));
